Sagittarius today: 

Jellyfish survived five mass extinctions. You may face some difficulties, but you are perfectly ready to stand up for yourself and take a new course if necessary. Whichever way the tide takes you, you are now sure that you will be all right and have proper abilities to succeed. (www.astrology-zodiac-signs.com).
